titles.title: Honoring the life, service, and accomplishments of General Robert H. Barrow, United States Marine Corps.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Armed Services.

bill.summary:
2/10/2009--Introduced.
Honors General Robert H. Barrow for his 41 years of service to the United States, and commends him for his dedication and commitment to excellence as a Marine and leader of Marines.
